                       von REXXOPT 1.7 (9.1.95) © by PROXITY SOFTWORKS
                         * FontLook-Auto.fwrexx.long - normal    (7894 Bytes)
                         * FontLook-Auto.fwrexx      - optimiert (6032 Bytes)

